title: 7@N - 20 Minutes - Live Is Life 2013

*****************         *****************

Thanx for downloading one of my mixes / Mixtapes, hope you enjoy to hear them as much as i do making them ;D

Been a Deejay for over 20 years, and ill never stop burning for the music, no matter how old i get, no matter what shape or form ill be in.
I live in Sweden and used to spin records on a professional level, but when i got older and got a family and kids, i had to take a step back, but i never stop beeing a deejay.
If you have it in youre blood, dont let go, no matter what people tell you or how they behave.

You can follow me on different channels!

Mixcloud / 7anDJ / Klubb Kidz

Thnx for the support and kind words over the years

Take care yall and catch ya l8r!
